-- Peugeot Close to Combining German Sites, Handelsblatt Reports
-- B y   N i c h o l a s   C o m f o r t
-- 2012-03-27T18:33:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-27/peugeot-close-to-combining-german-sites-handelsblatt-reports.html
PSA Peugeot Citroen SA (UG)  will
probably decide to combine the German headquarters of Peugeot
and Citroen in coming days, Handelsblatt reported, citing an
unidentified person familiar with the matter.  Citroen’s German unit is based in Cologne while Peugeot’s
operations in the country are based in Saarbruecken, the
newspaper said in an e-mailed summary of an article to be
published tomorrow.  The combined headquarters will be in Cologne, Handelsblatt
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nicholas Comfort in Frankfurt at 
 ncomfort1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
